threepio.engine
Class TablerController

java.lang.Object
  threepio.engine.TablerController

public class TablerController
extends java.lang.Object

TablerController makes use of the Tabler, by wrapping it, in order to make a full table, with versioned rows reflecting the progression from a base document to the specified document.

Author:
jhoule
See Also:
